  "title": "Devotional: Men Called to Lead",
  "body": "Men must first lead in their homes, then in their communities. Leadership is not about power, but about sacrifice, service, and faithfulness.\n\nJesus showed us meekness and humility. John showed us faithful love. The call is to pick up the cross, to lead with love and courage, to stand firm in faith.",
